<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 12:28:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2bfb71296e5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;金凤花&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The flower of a buttercup in the grass. The sun is shining and the petals are shining in the sun and you can understand why this flower bears this name." height="2004" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a2bfb71296e5.jpg" width="2004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 12:28:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2b28e9caa30</link><description>&lt;p&gt;神秘学&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="occult" height="4000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pmurad/6a2b28e9caa30.jpg" width="1848"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pmurad.some.pics"&gt;@pmurad&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 21:30:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>宙斯与伽倪墨得斯</title><link>https://some.pics/6a2b26e7041e2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;宙斯与伽倪墨得&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Zeus and Ganymede" height="1772" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/kdpartworks/6a2b26e7041e2.jpg" width="1772"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://kdpartworks.some.pics"&gt;@kdpartworks&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 21:21:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2ae6ce1dfb0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;您好，请提供您需要翻译的英文段落。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A path through a dense green hedge. East Modernist facade in the back, and a bright sunlit walkway crossing in front." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a2ae6ce1dfb0.jpg" width="1128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:48:16 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2ade1702542</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天我沿着风景优美的路线去了另一个村庄，途中经过了这座小教堂。它始建于13世纪20年代，位于从奥斯陆到特隆赫姆的一条朝圣路线上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small Romanesque-style church made of brick and black wooden roofs with a tiny bell tower in the middle of the main nave. It stands on a small hill surrounded by grass and trees. The sky is blue with just one small cotton cloud." height="2934" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a2ade1702542.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:11:06 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>